      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with the dreams and the energy—died a long time ago. now i'm just... going through the motions. like a ghost inhabiting a body that doesn't belong to me anymore. i'm just a walking corpse.",
